description: INV 28 NCUs 61 and 62 indicate stuck eastwards
completion_notes: Snow stow fault on NCUs 61 & 62. Snow sensor was dirty and cleaned. Fault cleared and SPCs returned to normal.

description: INV 28 NCUs 61 and 62 indicate stuck eastwards
completion_notes: A snow stow fault appeared on NCU's 61 & 62 located at inverter 28. All SPC's were stuck to the east. RES discovered that the snow sensor was dirty from vegetation management and construction. RES cleaned the snow sensor. The fault cleared on the NCU and all SPC's returned to normal operation.
